title: B.P.R.D. Issues complete to 2014
description:
This is the repeat of an earlier upload I did in 2012, but complete to 8/2014.

 I don't think I am missing anything B.P.R.D. related, but if I am let em know and I  will update if I can get the item. 

 I hope many of you will be able to complete your collections from this, as I see much of the older stuff is not longer available.

 I hope to uploading some of the great older comics I have, I have a lot of old stuff going back 10 years or more that I had gotten from Demonoid, and do not appear here, or anywhere else I searched.

 Please Note - the last group 35 - the Broken Equation is not out yet, I just set up the folder in advance.
 
  The list is based on the order from the Hellboy 

Wiki.http://hellboy.wikia.com/wiki/The_Hellboy_Universe_Comics

 I don't collect the Hellboy comics, I only have a small handful of them.

 Hope you enjoy this!
